{"tid":1963543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有關抗爭與移民的研究問卷","createTime":"2020-04-08T08:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T08:17:27.000Z","uid":354510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78e75afc6942b2b999af298b6e28ae2ba9f5ec85","tid":1963543,"uid":354510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"您好! 我是理工大學應用社會科學助理教授呂青湖，現在進行一項有關抗爭與移民的研究。目的是理解香港人如何應對政治動盪。當中會問及有關您的政治立場、對最近發生「反送中」運動的想法、以及移民海外的可能性。不論您的立場是支持、反對、不關心、或不了解抗爭運動，都希望您能填寫這份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n此問卷大約需時15-20分鐘。受訪者年齡必須是18至65歲，香港永久居民，並且現居在香港。我們不會問及你個人或其他人參與抗爭的內容細節。此研究無需要您的個人資料(請不要留下名字, 身份証號碼等)。所有收集的資料只作研究用途。<br />\n<br />\n問卷限額為1000人。完成問卷後會得到$50百佳現金券。如果您同意參與, 請入：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com/&hellip;/SV_1TXv4LKH&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2FSV_1TXv4LKH%E2%80%A6&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=28ce07c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com/&hellip;/SV_1TXv4LKH&hellip;</a><br />\n<br />\n參與者的禮券將於數天後寄出。多謝你們的參與。當中有參與者希望捐出禮劵,煩請讓我們知道你們想向哪間機構作出捐贈,以幫助到有需要的人士(e.g. 好鄰舍北區教會醫肚行動、陸陸雞煲、龍門,公益金,etc)。<br />\n<br />\n如果你還沒有參與這份問卷,我們希望你能夠抽空參與!<br />\n<br />\n萬分多謝!!!"},{"pid":"cb52488e1a53dabd8465daa606c184786e9dff21","tid":1963543,"uid":281501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"403 Forbidden"},{"pid":"2cfcc24e84145f6c56c06806a5f46db52b15e740","tid":1963543,"uid":354510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T08:16:16.000Z","msg":"條link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_1TXv4LKHLSPBosR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_1TXv4LKHLSPBosR&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=436b8dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_